en_175090_0	Former Deputy Minister Shantha Premaratne, who was from Ampara, has been sentenced to a 4-year rigorous imprisonment.
en_175090_1	Colombo High Court Judge, Piyasena Ranasinghe delivered the verdict today (09) when a case against the former Deputy Minister was taken up.
en_175090_2	The former Deputy Minister was accused of demanding and obtaining Rs.
en_175090_3	50,000 bribe from a woman in Ampara in 2007.
en_175090_4	He was also ordered to pay a fine of Rs.
en_175090_5	10,000.
